{"tid":1663284,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"黑警已成功以XRY軟件讀取並複製","createTime":"2019-10-19T10:23:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-20T11:36:32.000Z","uid":281029,"like":9,"dislike":49,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"98c88ea138a3a5323293d619e3de737b3c991e16","tid":1663284,"uid":281029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T10:23:39.000Z","msg":"#新聞 #公告 <br />\n警方已成功破解iPhone<br />\n有消息人士指，警方已成功以XRY軟件讀取並複製被捕人士之iOS device內所儲存的資訊。<br />\n<br />\n其於手機內，甚至於iCloud內儲存的資料亦被成功復原，包括並不限於location data，通訊記錄。<br />\n<br />\n而就通訊軟件，如telegram內的&quot;Secret Chat&quot; 以至於已被刪除的chatroom亦能成功追溯。<br />\n<br />\n本頻道在此作出呼籲，請所有人，包括已被捕但獲保釋人士:<br />\n1.  立即刪除原iCloud帳戶或更改密碼;<br />\n2. 更改所有雙重認證碼;<br />\n3. 去電訊公司為simcard加sim lock;<br />\n4. 將iOS更新至最新版本;<br />\n5. 去信Telegram/Apple總公司，希望其就事件提供應變措施。<br />\n<br />\n軟件developer/公司CEO發言如下: <br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/35Lb2QM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F35Lb2QM&d=om99xhx1cOxPLv9Q%2FbR%2FoFNDr8uFEZb%2F0ofPPvrEBCw%3D&h=56d60f44\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/35Lb2QM</a>"},{"pid":"c99b5052a499ee9ba0c92b66d00fd3e8020cf890","tid":1663284,"uid":47605,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T10:23:56.000Z","msg":"【1020 尖咀見】真。遊行指南參考<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <a href=\"https://lih.kg/aksjJwU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/aksjJwU</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4371ebcb390139d2688b181909b45f583ca7fab5","tid":1663284,"uid":128352,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T10:24:44.000Z","msg":"唔知咩黎 先推"},{"pid":"61138a1c4a94bf9e6318278bbe64bdfffae8e7ea","tid":1663284,"uid":145974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T10:26:54.000Z","msg":"推！！！"},{"pid":"9cf43d913c56b655d2b93a159c75eee3f8e425aa","tid":1663284,"uid":168366,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T10:29:50.000Z","msg":"呢個apple唔會唔理 (因為FBI都會用到)<br />\nApple未做野前大家小心"},{"pid":"565437e18003f354c8e491192fc38f1b3eceb5ec","tid":1663284,"uid":249794,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T10:38:30.000Z","msg":"俄仔都未解到telegram 班狗憑咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5574cc77f7e90af3517c0512bcff569d2f72281c","tid":1663284,"uid":26618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T10:45:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"24e061ef6bcf5222d544f8432eca28d6010c36ed","tid":1663284,"uid":14897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T11:01:54.000Z","msg":"推 小心為上 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eef53462cddef31c458205d7fec9cfc397477a1f","tid":1663284,"uid":43493,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T11:09:24.000Z","msg":"驚"},{"pid":"cf7f7837378079de7ec84c1f98e4793c3d0f9b93","tid":1663284,"uid":34779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9cf43d913c56b655d2b93a159c75eee3f8e425aa","tid":1663284,"uid":168366,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T10:29:50.000Z","msg":"呢個apple唔會唔理 (因為FBI都會用到)<br />\nApple未做野前大家小心"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T11:10:13.000Z","msg":"其實apple冇嘢可以做到，apple A5 至 A11比人搵到hardware漏洞，冇得patch, 即係iPhone X及先前出嘅iPhone都中招"},{"pid":"be25b923d67f13bf0aab88f30697f93bb9fe6015","tid":1663284,"uid":19005,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T11:10:53.000Z","msg":"source?<br />\nfbi餓客都破唔到幾時到香港破解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b62c58135524c0babf8ddbd69dbf1a1ffff9e6d","tid":1663284,"uid":88829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T11:20:09.000Z","msg":"有冇咁撚勁呀"},{"pid":"656fff8ff11cf1239ac642df71a6d452a136a05f","tid":1663284,"uid":68,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T11:20:46.000Z","msg":"fbi都唔得香港政府得？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"993137ae335cf3a71847b2bf81e747c5049451e3","tid":1663284,"uid":23094,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T11:21:23.000Z","msg":"IT Popo有咁勁就唔使做Popo啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7af6d1c5ff112ea069f1f77efdc0f582ce8df99e","tid":1663284,"uid":236368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T11:21:40.000Z","msg":"第5點好撚on9，apple奶共已經世界第一"},{"pid":"fd7a6891e12e668e144814439b33c4c73b11e67c","tid":1663284,"uid":13689,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T11:22:42.000Z","msg":"&gt; 如telegram內的&quot;Secret Chat&quot; 以至於已被刪除的chatroom亦能成功追溯。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"544c198cfa4bc2b623fcdd1cc410d65769accc18","tid":1663284,"uid":109712,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T11:25:09.000Z","msg":"其實冇人講係popo破，係話popo用XRY extract到data喎<br />\n<br />\nGoogle咗一陣XRY，似乎係某啲condition下真係可以由locked iphone extract到data。但android因為太多廠做，間間都有唔同的customization，變咗破到的唔多"},{"pid":"4d3e7e67b158147e95bc80e54a4c79a2428ad4d6","tid":1663284,"uid":41317,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"993137ae335cf3a71847b2bf81e747c5049451e3","tid":1663284,"uid":23094,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T11:21:23.000Z","msg":"IT Popo有咁勁就唔使做Popo啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T11:25:25.000Z","msg":"應該係買"},{"pid":"420361108cbd688c3d642b12ea49787853f8328c","tid":1663284,"uid":12251,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T11:28:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">未有成功 case</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.theverge.com/2019/9/27/20886835/iphone-exploit-checkm8-axi0mx-security-flaw-vunerability-jailbreak-permanent-bootrom-ios\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2F2019%2F9%2F27%2F20886835%2Fiphone-exploit-checkm8-axi0mx-security-flaw-vunerability-jailbreak-permanent-bootrom-ios&d=om99xhx1cOxPLv9Q%2FbR%2FoFNDr8uFEZb%2F0ofPPvrEBCw%3D&h=2fddb847\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.theverge.com/2019/9/27/20886835/iphone-exploit-checkm8-axi0mx-security-flaw-vunerability-jailbreak-permanent-bootrom-ios</a>"},{"pid":"176141380f99010c2be93f23174af39363a338b9","tid":1663284,"uid":281029,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"98c88ea138a3a5323293d619e3de737b3c991e16","tid":1663284,"uid":281029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T10:23:39.000Z","msg":"#新聞 #公告 <br />\n警方已成功破解iPhone<br />\n有消息人士指，警方已成功以XRY軟件讀取並複製被捕人士之iOS device內所儲存的資訊。<br />\n<br />\n其於手機內，甚至於iCloud內儲存的資料亦被成功復原，包括並不限於location data，通訊記錄。<br />\n<br />\n而就通訊軟件，如telegram內的&quot;Secret Chat&quot; 以至於已被刪除的chatroom亦能成功追溯。<br />\n<br />\n本頻道在此作出呼籲，請所有人，包括已被捕但獲保釋人士:<br />\n1.  立即刪除原iCloud帳戶或更改密碼;<br />\n2. 更改所有雙重認證碼;<br />\n3. 去電訊公司為simcard加sim lock;<br />\n4. 將iOS更新至最新版本;<br />\n5. 去信Telegram/Apple總公司，希望其就事件提供應變措施。<br />\n<br />\n軟件developer/公司CEO發言如下: <br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/35Lb2QM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F35Lb2QM&d=om99xhx1cOxPLv9Q%2FbR%2FoFNDr8uFEZb%2F0ofPPvrEBCw%3D&h=56d60f44\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/35Lb2QM</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T12:33:33.000Z","msg":"#澄清<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/frontlinelive/28481\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ffrontlinelive%2F28481&d=om99xhx1cOxPLv9Q%2FbR%2FoFNDr8uFEZb%2F0ofPPvrEBCw%3D&h=ca66cc1b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/frontlinelive/28481</a><br />\n上文文末所提及的CEO感言與正文並無關係，只是讓大眾了解何為XRY軟件。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，警方所使用的破解技術與CIA或FBI不同，並非解鎖電話，而是bypass電話本身的encryption，直接讀取並複製資料至另一部device。<br />\n<br />\n此類技術一早已有小道消息流出: <br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2P4ORiz\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2P4ORiz&d=om99xhx1cOxPLv9Q%2FbR%2FoFNDr8uFEZb%2F0ofPPvrEBCw%3D&h=7cd7cb68\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2P4ORiz</a><br />\n... police forces and federal agencies across the country have purchased relatively cheap tools to unlock up-to-date iPhones, bypassing their encryption. <br />\n警方亦能自被破解的裝置上讀取你儲存於電話上的keychain, 從而進入你的iCloud。<br />\n<br />\n另外，明白到有FBI舊例在先，香港人一直誤以為iPhone為絕對安全。實際上，就2015年FBI與蘋果公司對立一案，FBI最後亦成功解鎖電話，取得資訊。<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/33HK8Yc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F33HK8Yc&d=om99xhx1cOxPLv9Q%2FbR%2FoFNDr8uFEZb%2F0ofPPvrEBCw%3D&h=3a9f1781\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/33HK8Yc</a><br />\n... later the Federal Bureau of Investigation reportedly paid over a million dollars to a vendor for unlocking the shooter's iPhone.<br />\n<br />\n最後就Telegram被破解一事，admin並無足夠IT知識去為大家作解釋。但Telegram使用的MTProto並否為一眾Cryptographer所泛用，加上Telegram所使用的end-to-end encryption並不會將資料儲存至server, 而是會留在local decive, 亦能解釋到為何警方破解電話資料便能讀取Telegram。<br />\nMIT曾有研究人員就Telegram並不如大家想像中安全作解釋，其研究報告如下:<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2gVje93\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2gVje93&d=om99xhx1cOxPLv9Q%2FbR%2FoFNDr8uFEZb%2F0ofPPvrEBCw%3D&h=cfb03dc4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2gVje93</a><br />\n<br />\n本台秉持着實事求事的精神，對所有發放的資訊皆會先行查證。惟是次事關重大，牽連甚廣，恕本台無法通報消息來源。但空穴來風，未必無因，請各位務必認真看待，把本台於上文中建議的五項行動作為一項預防措施。"},{"pid":"03956ef29df889a713f760f8bdb7a5d979f65c52","tid":1663284,"uid":61032,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T13:06:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\">甚至於iCloud內儲存的資料亦被成功復原</span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc43870db50077c64081e5db613616c6a70172ca","tid":1663284,"uid":58104,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T13:29:19.000Z","msg":"推你老母咩 咪on9啦 成班智障<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f00c609717b5506ef2fc5c13d41ff5f22081abf","tid":1663284,"uid":92734,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"565437e18003f354c8e491192fc38f1b3eceb5ec","tid":1663284,"uid":249794,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T10:38:30.000Z","msg":"俄仔都未解到telegram 班狗憑咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T13:34:14.000Z","msg":"而就通訊軟件，如telegram內的&quot;Secret Chat&quot; 以至於已被刪除的chatroom亦能成功追溯。&lt;&lt; <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咪係 , 無留底, 完全消失既野點追溯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 九up"},{"pid":"163ba2622a9dbb6749a61e529eccbd3768442cd3","tid":1663284,"uid":151933,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T13:37:03.000Z","msg":"又話iphone好安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"712ce2f6c0d9289999738de2ff721bc1db87f775","tid":1663284,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"176141380f99010c2be93f23174af39363a338b9","tid":1663284,"uid":281029,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"98c88ea138a3a5323293d619e3de737b3c991e16","tid":1663284,"uid":281029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T10:23:39.000Z","msg":"#新聞 #公告 <br />\n警方已成功破解iPhone<br />\n有消息人士指，警方已成功以XRY軟件讀取並複製被捕人士之iOS device內所儲存的資訊。<br />\n<br />\n其於手機內，甚至於iCloud內儲存的資料亦被成功復原，包括並不限於location data，通訊記錄。<br />\n<br />\n而就通訊軟件，如telegram內的&quot;Secret Chat&quot; 以至於已被刪除的chatroom亦能成功追溯。<br />\n<br />\n本頻道在此作出呼籲，請所有人，包括已被捕但獲保釋人士:<br />\n1.  立即刪除原iCloud帳戶或更改密碼;<br />\n2. 更改所有雙重認證碼;<br />\n3. 去電訊公司為simcard加sim lock;<br />\n4. 將iOS更新至最新版本;<br />\n5. 去信Telegram/Apple總公司，希望其就事件提供應變措施。<br />\n<br />\n軟件developer/公司CEO發言如下: <br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/35Lb2QM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F35Lb2QM&d=om99xhx1cOxPLv9Q%2FbR%2FoFNDr8uFEZb%2F0ofPPvrEBCw%3D&h=56d60f44\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/35Lb2QM</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T12:33:33.000Z","msg":"#澄清<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/frontlinelive/28481\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ffrontlinelive%2F28481&d=om99xhx1cOxPLv9Q%2FbR%2FoFNDr8uFEZb%2F0ofPPvrEBCw%3D&h=ca66cc1b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/frontlinelive/28481</a><br />\n上文文末所提及的CEO感言與正文並無關係，只是讓大眾了解何為XRY軟件。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，警方所使用的破解技術與CIA或FBI不同，並非解鎖電話，而是bypass電話本身的encryption，直接讀取並複製資料至另一部device。<br />\n<br />\n此類技術一早已有小道消息流出: <br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2P4ORiz\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2P4ORiz&d=om99xhx1cOxPLv9Q%2FbR%2FoFNDr8uFEZb%2F0ofPPvrEBCw%3D&h=7cd7cb68\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2P4ORiz</a><br />\n... police forces and federal agencies across the country have purchased relatively cheap tools to unlock up-to-date iPhones, bypassing their encryption. <br />\n警方亦能自被破解的裝置上讀取你儲存於電話上的keychain, 從而進入你的iCloud。<br />\n<br />\n另外，明白到有FBI舊例在先，香港人一直誤以為iPhone為絕對安全。實際上，就2015年FBI與蘋果公司對立一案，FBI最後亦成功解鎖電話，取得資訊。<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/33HK8Yc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F33HK8Yc&d=om99xhx1cOxPLv9Q%2FbR%2FoFNDr8uFEZb%2F0ofPPvrEBCw%3D&h=3a9f1781\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/33HK8Yc</a><br />\n... later the Federal Bureau of Investigation reportedly paid over a million dollars to a vendor for unlocking the shooter's iPhone.<br />\n<br />\n最後就Telegram被破解一事，admin並無足夠IT知識去為大家作解釋。但Telegram使用的MTProto並否為一眾Cryptographer所泛用，加上Telegram所使用的end-to-end encryption並不會將資料儲存至server, 而是會留在local decive, 亦能解釋到為何警方破解電話資料便能讀取Telegram。<br />\nMIT曾有研究人員就Telegram並不如大家想像中安全作解釋，其研究報告如下:<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2gVje93\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2gVje93&d=om99xhx1cOxPLv9Q%2FbR%2FoFNDr8uFEZb%2F0ofPPvrEBCw%3D&h=cfb03dc4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2gVje93</a><br />\n<br />\n本台秉持着實事求事的精神，對所有發放的資訊皆會先行查證。惟是次事關重大，牽連甚廣，恕本台無法通報消息來源。但空穴來風，未必無因，請各位務必認真看待，把本台於上文中建議的五項行動作為一項預防措施。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T14:18:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">bypass電話本身的encryption，直接讀取並複製資料至另一部device</span><br />\n<br />\nencryption同password識分未呀智障<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}